---
title: Glazed Honey-Garlic Chicken Thighs with Bok Choy and Cashews
description: Did someone say sticky chicken? The sweet and savoury combination of soy, honey, ginger and garlic makes a delicious glaze. The glazed chicken is plated over a bed of rice with pops of bok choy. Cashews finish this dish off with a satisfying crunch!
